<p>Ok, back to the JavaScript! Add <code>var $wrapper = </code> then use <code>jQuery</code> to select that
wrapper element. Register a listener on <code>click</code> for any <code>.js-remove-scientist</code>
element - that's the delete link. Start that function with my favorite <code>e.preventDefault()</code>:</p>
